name: Low Poly Street Lamp Pack (Recolorable)
description:
Six low poly street lamps separated into different parts for easy recoloring in ROBLOX studio (or other). Please do not reupload/resell and do let me know if you have any issues. Below are their tris (from left to right).

  • Lamp 1 - 494 triangles
  • Lamp 2 - 398 triangles
  • Lamp 3 - 446 triangles
  • Lamp 4 - 590 triangles
  • Lamp 5 - 590 triangles
  • Lamp 6 - 604 triangles
